  <p>
    These days I am focused on improving my skills, building more intentionally, and exploring what is next, trying to achieve something real. For a long time I chased unique things across every corner of the internet, Reddit, Discord, and X.

    I wanted to solve problems and build something unique, but one of my internet mentors told me that uniqueness takes time. To master the art, you must first learn the old ways.

    i often ask myself what is something i'm really proud of. Not yet. But soon.
  </p>

